s==\n* [http://www.siima.in/nomination.php Official website]\n\n[[Category:SIIMA Awards]]\n[[Category:2018 Indian film awards]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox film awards\n| number              = 7\n| award               = SIIMA Awards\n| award_link          = South Indian International Movie Awards\n| type                = \n| image               = \n| caption             = \n| date                = September 14 \u2013 15, 2018\n| site                =  [[Dubai]]\n| producer            = \n| director            = \n| organizer           = \n| best_picture        = \n| best_direction      = \n| best_direction_film = \n| best_actor          = \n| best_actor_film     = \n| best_actress        = \n| best_actress_film   = \n| most_wins           = \n| most_nominations    = \n| channel             = \n| network             =  [[Sun TV Network]]\n| duration            = \n| ratings             = \n| last                = [[6th South Indian International Movie Awards|6th]]\n| next                = [[8th South Indian International Movie Awards|8th]]\n}}\n\nThe '''7th South Indian International Movie Awards''' is an awards event held at [[Dubai]] on September 14th and 15th, 2018.<ref>[https://m.dailyhunt.in/news/india/english/telugu+bullet+english-epaper-telbulen/siima+awards+2018+dates+and+venue+confirmed-newsid-92461938 SIIMA Awards 2018 Dates and Venue Confirmed]</ref> [[South Indian International Movie Awards|SIIMA]] 2018 will recognize the best films and performances from the past year in [[Tamil cinema|Tamil]], [[Malayalam cinema|Malayalam]], [[Telugu cinema|Telugu]], and [[Kannada cinema|Kannada]] films along with special honors for lifetime contributions and a few special awards.<ref>{{cite web|title=Nominations list for the SIIMA 2017 announced!|url=http://www.sify.com/movies/nominations-list-for-the-siima-2017-announced-news-tnpl-rgbk0Mbjijgdf.html|work=Sify.com}}</ref> The nomination list for the main awards was announced in June 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sify.com/movies/siima-awards-2017-nominations-announced-news-malayalam-rgbjE9ecgbbif.html|title=SIIMA awards 2017 nominations announced|publisher=Sify.com}}</ref>\n\n== Honorary awards  ==\n*[[P. Suseela]] (Lifetime Achievement)\n\n== Main awards winners and nominees ==\n<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ibtimes.co.in/siima-awards-2018-telugu-kannada-nomination-list-out-date-place-7th-edition-revealed-777016|title=SIIMA Awards 2018 - Telugu, Kannada nomination list out|website=International Business Times|date=5 August 2018|access-date=19 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/siima-2018-nominations-vijays-mersal-beats-madhavan-and-vijay-sethupathis-vikram-vedha-1901012|title=SIIMA 2018 Nominations: Vijay's Mersal Beats Madhavan And Vijay Sethupathi's Vikram Vedha|website=NDTV|date=15 August 2018|access-date=19 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ibtimes.co.in/siima-awards-live-update-check-out-see-tollywood-sandalwood-winners-list-780619|title=SIIMA Awards 2018 Telugu Kannada winners list|website=International Business Times|date=16 September 2018|access-date=19 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ibtimes.co.in/siima-awards-2018-tamil-winners-list-photos-vijays-mersal-tops-list-5-honours-780694|title=SIIMA Awards 2018 \u2013 Tamil winners list|website=International Business Times|date=16 September 2018|access-date=19 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/regional-movies/siima-2018-sivakartikeyan-nivin-pauly-r-madhavan-hansika-motwani-win-big-on-day-1/story-QEaUgz81IrHcCSUt3gXcEJ.html|title=SIIMA 2018: Sivakartikeyan, Nivin Pauly, R Madhavan, Hansika Motwani win big on day 1|website=Hindustan Times|date=15 September 2018|access-date=19 January 2020}}</ref>\n=== Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" |\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" ! style=\"background:#eedd82; width:3000px; text-align:center;\"|<big>Best Film</big>\n|-\n! ! style=\"background:#efac00; width:50%; text-align:center;\"|Ta