aveen]] \u2013 ''[[Sathamanam Bhavati]]''\n**[[Prudhviraj]] \u2013 ''[[PSV Garuda Vega]]''\n**Shakalaka Shankar \u2013 ''[[Anando Brahma]]''\n**[[Srinivas Reddy]] \u2013 ''[[Anando Brahma]]'' / ''[[Raja The Great]]''\n\n|-\n! ! style=\"background:#00def3; text-align:center;\"| Kannada\n! ! style=\"background:#4df300; text-align:center;\"| Malayalam\n|-\n|\n**[[Chikkanna]] \u2013 ''[[Raajakumara]]''\n**[[Kuri Prathap]] \u2013 ''[[Melkote Manja]]''\n**[[Sadhu Kokila]] \u2013 ''[[Chamak]]''\n**[[Saikumar Pudipeddi|Saikumar]] \u2013 ''[[Happy New Year (2017 film)|Happy New Year]]''\n**Vijay Chendur \u2013 ''[[Pataki (film)|Pataki]]''\n| \n**[[Aju Varghese]] \u2013 ''[[Godha]]''\n**[[Dharmajan]] \u2013 ''[[Punyalan Private Limited]]''\n**[[Hareesh Perumanna]] \u2013 ''[[Rakshadhikari Baiju Oppu]]''\n**[[Jacob Gregory]] \u2013 ''[[Jomonte Suvisheshangal]]''\n**[[Saiju Kurup]]\u2013 ''[[Aadu 2]]''\n|}\n\n=== Debut awards ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" |\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" ! style=\"background:#eedd82; width:3000px; text-align:center;\"|<big>'''SIIMA Award for Best Debut Actor'''</big>\n|-\n! ! style=\"background:#efac00; width:50%; text-align:center;\"|Tamil\n! ! style=\"background:#efeb00; width:50%; text-align:center;\"|Telugu\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''[[Vasanth Ravi]]''' \u2013 '''''[[Taramani (film)|Taramani]]'''''\n**[[Hiphop Tamizha]] \u2013 ''[[Meesaya Murukku]]'' \n**[[Vetri (cinematographer)|Vetri]] \u2013 ''[[8 Thottakkal]]'' \n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''Ishaan''' \u2013 '''''[[Rogue (2017 film)|Rogue]]'''''\n**Aashish Raj \u2013 ''[[Aakatayi]]''\n**Ganta Ravi \u2013 ''Jayadev''\n**Rakshit \u2013 ''[[London Babulu]]''\n**Vishwaksen \u2013 ''Vellipomakey''\n|-\n! ! style=\"background:#00def3; text-align:center;\"| Kannada\n! ! style=\"background:#4df300; text-align:center;\"| Malayalam\n|-\n|\n*'''[[Rishi (Kannada actor)|Rishi]]''' \u2013 '''''[[Operation Alamelamma]]'''''\n**Ishaan \u2013 ''[[Rogue (2017 film)|Rogue]]''\n**[[Manoranjan]] \u2013 ''[[Saheba (film)|S